{"tid":759640,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"杜慈：阿仙奴踢歐霸，對嗎？","createTime":"2018-07-28T20:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T08:03:10.000Z","uid":186431,"like":34,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"3414905ca08f215b5e3f4f6e7ef491fe9a09c3b6","tid":759640,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T20:15:16.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=644124c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】巴黎聖日耳門被阿仙奴大敗，主帥杜慈賽後發表的一番言論似若有所指。<br />\n<br />\n周六在新加坡國家體育場上演的國際冠軍盃，阿仙奴的奧斯爾早段取得士哥再加上拿卡錫迪梅開二度，倒戈的新帥艾美利終帶領兵工廠以5:1大勝巴黎聖日耳門。PSG主帥杜慈吃了悶棍後，被問到阿仙奴人腳比缺少多名世界盃國腳的PSG完整，是否勝負關鍵時說得明白。<br />\n<br />\n「是的，顯然是。」他續說：「我認為他們本季是出戰歐霸盃，對嗎？」到底他是想表明阿仙奴的實力不該參與歐洲「第2盃賽」？還是有意無意揭人傷疤？此話的實際用意，或許只有他自己知。"},{"pid":"77e2e69fbabfd071b2e902d0274576de570a66a3","tid":759640,"uid":46151,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T20:19:13.000Z","msg":"佢意思係歐霸隊都贏到PSG下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c731b0df9e2ead95c14404a0bbcf5432cac873","tid":759640,"uid":186431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"77e2e69fbabfd071b2e902d0274576de570a66a3","tid":759640,"uid":46151,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T20:19:13.000Z","msg":"佢意思係歐霸隊都贏到PSG下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T20:31:16.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴5：1大破PSG 杜慈：睇陣容已經知輸梗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87efa9b1b9eb75bf8547b50162d45ea7b97c4c88","tid":759640,"uid":90726,"like"